// App Gateway - Active Instance IDs (Last 24 Hours)
// Lists every distinct App Gateway instance that handled at least one request
// in the past 24 hours. Use this as a quick inventory of how many instances
// were active, and to cross-reference instance IDs with other queries.
AGWAccessLogs
| where TimeGenerated > ago(24h)
| distinct InstanceId
| order by InstanceId asc